  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This retrospective chart review will demonstrate the feasibility of performing caudal
      epidural blockade in adolescents undergoing major orthopedic hip surgery and provide
      information regarding the feasibility of this technique's use on a regular basis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
